handa na,

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:23.520
kasama si Officer Xia.

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:24.079
gusto mo ba?

00:02:24.079 --> 00:02:24.880
Sandali lang.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:42.680
Wang,

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:44.010
Nandito na si Officer Wei.

